results.name: Signature permutation of a nonrecursive Catalan automorphism: row 1655089 of table A089840.
link: A. Karttunen, Prolog-program which illustrates the construction of this and other similar nonrecursive Catalan automorphisms.
Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
program: (Scheme function, destructive implementation of this automorphism acting on S-expressions:) (define (*A123497! s) (cond ((null? s) s) ((and (pair? (car s)) (pair? (cdar s))) (*A074680! s) (let ((old-cddr-s (cddr s))) (set-cdr! (cdr s) (cdadr s)) (set-cdr! (cadr s) old-cddr-s))) ((pair? (car s)) (*A072797! s)) ((pair? (cdr s)) (*A072796! s))) s)
xref: Inverse: A123498. Row 1655089 of A089840. Used to construct automorphism *A123501. A074680(n) = A083927(a(A057123(n))).
